Package: IST
Type: Package
Title: In Silico Treatment for Translating Between Animal Models and Humans
Description: The IST package enables the translation of molecular
    signatures between organisms, disease models or cell cultures.
    IST simulates how the effect on the experimental organism 
    translate into the target organism through orthology mapping.
Version: 0.5.30
Date: 2022-04-11
